⊥ (77.5 ± 1.7 μV/K) was obtained at the 8 wt% of Ag@NCDots. In addition, the through plane PF
⊥ ~109.0 ± 4 μV/mK2 and a through plane ZT⊥ ~0.148 ± 0.018 were achieved at 8 wt% of Ag@NCDots nanoparticles at room temperature. The in plane PF

